--- !u!114 &820919839
MonoBehaviour:
  m_ObjectHideFlags: 0
  m_CorrespondingSourceObject: {fileID: 0}
  m_PrefabInstance: {fileID: 0}
  m_PrefabAsset: {fileID: 0}
  m_GameObject: {fileID: 820919837}
  m_Enabled: 1
  m_EditorHideFlags: 0
  m_Script: {fileID: 11500000, guid: 5f372ca38a79b7c4f92b3bfce4f0b49d, type: 3}
  m_Name: 
  m_EditorClassIdentifier: Assembly-CSharp::PrologueController
  panels:
  - backgroundSprite: {fileID: 21300000, guid: ec9dcd324eabbfe4f85a0468c82a49b3, type: 3}
    speakerName: Siera
    bodyText: "Before Thornwall\u2026 the land was alive.\n\nWitches walked among
      the people, protecting the realm with their magic.\n\nThe world was bright.\nThe
      world was safe."
    showSieraPortrait: 1
  - backgroundSprite: {fileID: 21300000, guid: 42557ca1de3d12442af7cfe4f022369a, type: 3}
    speakerName: Siera
    bodyText: "Then Thornwall was awoken by the power hungry witch, Rakel.\n\nBound
      by a dark spell, the castle became sentient\u2026\nA living fortress that hungered
      for magic.\n\nOne by one\u2026 the covens fell."
    showSieraPortrait: 1
  - backgroundSprite: {fileID: 21300000, guid: cd40fb8e2d290164b855858528ce3432, type: 3}
    speakerName: Siera
    bodyText: "I am Siera\u2026\nThe last witch still free from Thornwall's grasp.\n\nFor
      years, I have worked in silence\u2026\nPreparing for this moment."
    showSieraPortrait: 1
  - backgroundSprite: {fileID: 21300000, guid: 816c13c14ebd9514596c7af9dedae4c4, type: 3}
    speakerName: Siera
    bodyText: "The Ember Flame ressistance still burns.\n\nDisguised as Thornwall's
      thralls, they wait inside its halls\u2026\nHidden allies\u2026 carrying the
      clues I will need.\n\nI will not face this alone."
    showSieraPortrait: 1
  - backgroundSprite: {fileID: 21300000, guid: 0efa6c411a000ae44ae92a011ca0ebc2, type: 3}
    speakerName: Siera
    bodyText: "Tonight\u2026 I enter Thornwall.\n\nI will navigate its catacombs\u2026\nIts
      gardens\u2026 Its corridors. its mazes it created to ensure the heart gate
      remains unreachable. \n\nBut i will get through\u2026 And I will end this curseand
      free those stuck in its grasp!"
    showSieraPortrait: 1
  - backgroundSprite: {fileID: 21300000, guid: e8c002d24eb0aae4388548f943e512d2, type: 3}
    speakerName: Siera
    bodyText: "But Thornwall is alive.\n\nIt watches.\nIt learns.\n\nIf my suspicion
      rises too high\u2026 The castle will see me for what I am, a source of magic
      to drain from within its dungeon walls. "
    showSieraPortrait: 1
  backgroundImage: {fileID: 1685951246}
  fadeOverlay: {fileID: 1221789484}
  sieraPortrait: {fileID: 1882953526}
  speakerNameText: {fileID: 828656087}
  bodyText: {fileID: 1164714644}
  continueButton: {fileID: 1533726591}
  continueButtonText: {fileID: 2106474892}
  fadeDuration: 0.6
